# Farmly Design System (required for UI work)

Full reference: `docs/design-system.md`

## North star
Modern **village atmosphere** — warm, earthy, cinematic, trustworthy. NOT beige SaaS, NOT Apple/Airbnb, NOT card catalogs.

## Colors
- Default page: `loam-100` / `bg-loam-100` — not flat cream everywhere
- `cream` / `bg-cream` = accent band only (`loam-200`)
- Greens: `moss-*` (forest = `moss-700`, forest-deep = `moss-900`)
- Warm: `hearth-*`, `clay`, `soil`, `wheat`
- Avoid `stone-*` as primary palette

## Layout
- Prefer **editorial rows** (`surface-ghost`, `editorial-row`) over `surface-card` grids on landing/marketing
- Use `surface-card` only for settings, forms, dashboards
- Alternate section tones: `parchment` → `meadow` → `hearth` → `depth`
- Media: `CinematicMedia` + green-brown scrims, not flat black overlays

## Typography
- Display: Newsreader (`editorial-serif`, `type-chapter`, `type-hero`)
- Body: Source Sans 3
- Kickers: `0.12em` tracking, `soil`/`clay` on light, `wheat` on dark

## Motion
- `ease-organic` for UI, `ease-cinematic` for reveals
- `slow-drift` on hero imagery only
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`

## CTAs
- One primary per viewport; exploration via `story-link` (quiet)
- Invite copy, not "Shop now" / "Get started"

## Tokens
CSS: `src/styles/farmly-*.css` · TS: `src/lib/design/tokens.ts`
